fulltitle: Robert Parry: Aid to Nicaraguan Contras
album: Haydn: Three Favorite Concertos -- Cello, Violin & Trumpet Concertos - Expanded Edition
description:
http://www.c-span.org/video/?126-1/aid-nicaraguan-contras

Robert Parry, a correspondent for Newsweek, answered host and caller questions on the federal aid to the Contra rebels in Nicaragua. The Congress was heavily split on the issue as there was a peace process already underway at the time.

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
